{"tid":597547,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"被忽視的最本土港產片《中英街1號》","createTime":"2018-03-18T17:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T13:04:50.000Z","uid":72745,"like":100,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5d9dbc692ebc8aa1bce0f1c8bb8324234d92b9f3","tid":597547,"uid":72745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T17:35:27.000Z","msg":"由趙崇基執導、以六七暴動為背景發展到19年社會運動為題材的《中英街1號》以黑白拍攝，諷刺現今社會非黑即白，或者黑白不分的荒誕現象，故事分兩節，分別是1967年香港六七暴動，以及2019年另一場社會運動。趙崇基去年受訪時，表示申請政府電影發展基金遭拒。<br />\n<br />\n近日於第13屆大阪亞洲電影節榮獲<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最優秀作品獎（THE GRAND PRIX），該獎榮譽等同最佳電影，係競賽部份中的最大獎項</span></span>。去年此獎由黃進執導作品《一念無明》奪得。另外喺公佈嘅15套入圍電影名單中，有另外兩部港片，包括今屆香港電影金像獎有6項提名、杜汶澤自導自演的《空手道》；由譚惠貞執導，劉嘉玲與吳肇軒主演嘅《以青春的名義》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=458r-r6j_fg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D458r-r6j_fg&d=52AdeQVoG0iHqhOlgsm1sv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=c388f09f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=458r-r6j_fg</a><br />\n<br />\n更多《中英街1號》資訊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/no.1chungyingstreet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fno.1chungyingstreet%2F&d=52AdeQVoG0iHqhOlgsm1sv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=958a8fcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/no.1chungyingstreet/</a><br />\n<br />\n此外，杜汶澤亦憑著自編自導自演的《空手道》獲得亞洲明星大獎，不過畀佢老婆趺撚爛左。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1214389392028306&amp;set=a.111122362355020.13557.100003717698520&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D1214389392028306%26set%3Da.111122362355020.13557.100003717698520%26type%3D3%26theater&d=52AdeQVoG0iHqhOlgsm1sv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=dfc133d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1214389392028306&amp;set=a.111122362355020.13557.100003717698520&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家欣賞荷里活電影既同時關注一下香港電影<br />\n香港並唔係冇好既電影,只係你地留意唔到<br />\n所以唔好再望住D濕鳩大陸合拍片之後話港產片已死<br />\n香港電影界仲有一班有良心唔係一味搵銀既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a54d6c7ddbd33ac3c03f2112e0d4b75f62bdca","tid":597547,"uid":72745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T17:36:30.000Z","msg":"支持香港電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9467e5ec58f6947f0f1702d72a3071e223154c72","tid":597547,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T17:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4275ad2b4f86687c9e04b6af3ca75d2716e7708","tid":597547,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T18:09:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 此外，杜汶澤亦憑著自編自導自演的《空手道》獲得亞洲明星大獎，不過畀佢老婆趺撚爛左。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1214389392028306&amp;set=a.111122362355020.13557.100003717698520&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D1214389392028306%26set%3Da.111122362355020.13557.100003717698520%26type%3D3%26theater&d=52AdeQVoG0iHqhOlgsm1sv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=dfc133d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1214389392028306&amp;set=a.111122362355020.13557.100003717698520&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2254a72611058bef0e5aaa337f18985dc467430c","tid":597547,"uid":129940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T18:19:05.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"f2b73111e7066fd7d0049ab4865ae414220ea8be","tid":597547,"uid":129940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4275ad2b4f86687c9e04b6af3ca75d2716e7708","tid":597547,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dis