-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/171287?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=entertainment</a>"},{"pid":"b4c34e3f33b2976c5726e5a6c577a55fc0bff527","tid":597547,"uid":6169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:49:33.000Z","msg":"香港電影萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a2464b9091e6223083321b55edc004bb16d63a","tid":597547,"uid":72745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"162179c8e0e1aedba6b8067ac68cdae2a16c6d00","tid":597547,"uid":71283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:40:05.000Z","msg":"剛剛睇到呢篇文，導演真係好值得大家支持呀！<br />\n<br />\n趙崇基導演：「當時有人建議不如申請電影發展基金，而電影發展基金入面亦有人叫我申請，大家都覺得這種題材很適宜申請。一個如此本土、講香港歷史的非商業電影，也實在需要政府支持。誰不知電影發展基金以『商業元素』不足這種荒謬的理由拒絕，我商業元素足又何必找政府支援呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「當時向政府申請時，剛巧是《十年》風波後不久，我難以不把兩件事聯想在一起。記得當時申請失敗後，我的一位電影發展基金委員朋友跟我說，其中一位『藍絲』委員把《中英街1號》的劇本評為0分。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/171287?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=entertainment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F171287%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dentertainment&d=52AdeQVoG0iHqhOlgsm1sv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=859411a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/171287?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=entertainment</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T13:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7adcfa915c1870cbcf6beee0e245a2132f40e442","tid":597547,"uid":6436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T13:17:28.000Z","msg":"[公投] 連登港產三寶最後五強出爐，請入嚟擺低你神聖的三票！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/603899/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/603899/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f25afa677c6397578a6cf564f